 PDF-processing functions that can be called on\nfrom other Python scripts. The software is free for open academic research, but\nrequires paid license for commercial use.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 30 Nov 2012 00:15:57 GMT"}],"update_date":"2013-03-15"}
